+## Overview
+
+Between 2026-05-02 and 2026-05-21, the company recorded 30 orders totaling $7,154.44 in revenue across four regions and four products. The average order was worth $238.48, while the median order value was $204.94, indicating a fairly balanced order distribution with a few larger purchases pulling the mean upward.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget led all products with $2,392.00 in revenue from only 16 units, reflecting its high unit price of $149.50. Widget followed at $2,118.94 from 106 units. Doohickey earned $1,513.00 from 17 units, and Sprocket contributed $1,130.50 despite selling the most units (238), because of its low $4.75 price point.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North was the strongest region at $2,176.35, followed by East at $1,830.79 and South at $1,732.48. West trailed at $1,414.82, roughly 35% below North. Revenue is reasonably spread, with no single region exceeding a third of the total.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Prioritize Gadget promotion: it generates the most revenue per unit, so even small volume gains meaningfully lift totals.
+- Investigate West's underperformance versus North; targeted sales outreach there offers the largest regional upside.
+- Bundle low-priced Sprockets with Widgets or Gadgets to convert Sprocket's high unit volume into higher order values.
